1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) - The paper focuses on image generation and spatial constraints, which are core topics in computer vision. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The proposed Spatially Constrained Generative Adversarial Network (SCGAN) is a machine learning model that uses adversarial training to generate images. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper involves the use of AI techniques to generate images with specific spatial constraints. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) - The paper deals with generating images, which is a core topic in computer graphics. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper involves the generation of multimedia content (images) using machine learning techniques.
